<div>   
<p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family: 宋体">今天四川甘孜泸定县发生</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">6.8</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">级地震后不久，几位同行通过微信发信息给我，希望了解下该震发生在哪个地震区？属于哪个断裂带？是什么事件？未来地震趋势如何？我逐一做了解答。下午</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">4</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">点多，<span style="background: white">北京广播电视台新闻广播某记者，围绕地震的预测与预警问题，电话采访我，我也做了简短的回答。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 200%;font-family: 宋体;background: white">鉴于上述同行的问题有一定的科学性和普遍性，故我把解答略作整理形成此文。至于记者的问题，不少人士知道答案，本文就不再赘述啦。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 200%;font-family: 宋体;background: white">据我所知，每当世界上有重大灾害事件或其他热点事件发生，不少爱好科学的网友第一时间会上科学网寻求解答。因此，我建议有关博主们针对这些事件从专业角度进行分析并撰写博文，以服务于社会。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family: 宋体">言归正传。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family: 宋体">据中国地震台网测定，北京时间</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">2022</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">年</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">9</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">月</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">5</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">日</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">12</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">时</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">52</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">分在四川省甘孜州泸定县（北纬</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">29.59°</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">，东经</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">102.08°</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">）发生</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">6.8</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">级地震，震源深度</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">16 km</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family: 宋体">该震发生在我们所划定的鲜水河地震区；根据其震中位置，我们初步确定该震的发震断裂为鲜水河断裂带（图</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">1</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height: 200%;font-family:宋体">）。根据我们提出的多锁固段脆性破裂理论【</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">1</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">】，可判断这次地震所属的事件类型与震后地震趋势。</span></p><p style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">鲜水河地震区地震构造图</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="line-height: 200%; "Times New Roman", serif;">1</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">日康定南</span><em><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">2</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">6</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">日炉霍</span><em><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">S</span></sub><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">7.9</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">地震，其分别发生在第</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">1</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">锁固段的体积膨胀点和峰值强度点，因而具有明确的物理意义。在确定最小有效性震级</span><em><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">v</span></sub><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: Roman", serif;">2</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">）。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center;line-height:200%"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt Roman',serif">1725.08.01-2022.09.05</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">之间</span></strong></p><p Roman',serif">CBS</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">与时间关系</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family: 宋体">根据我们提出的主震判识准则，可知</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">1973</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">年炉霍</span><em><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">S</span></sub><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">7.9</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">地震仅是一次标志性地震而非主震，鲜水河地震区存在第</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">2</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">锁固段，当其被加载至峰值强度点时，应发生下一次标志性地震。根据我们提出的震级约束条件，预判该未来标志性地震震级为</span><em><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">S</span></sub><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">7.9~8.3</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">；在该标志性地震发生前，该地震区还将发生多次不超过</span><em><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">S</span></sub><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">7.7</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">的预震【</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">2</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">】。由于今日发生的泸定县</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">6.8</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">级地震大于锁固段破裂门槛震级</span><em><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">v</span></sub><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">（</span><em><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">S</span></sub><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">5.5</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height: 200%;font-family:宋体">），故确认该震为第</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">2</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">锁固段破裂事件，是一次预期的预震。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family: 宋体">截止到</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">2022</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">年</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">9</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height: 200%;font-family:宋体">月</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">5</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height: 200%;font-family:宋体">日，该地震区</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">CBS</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">监测值约为</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">3.70</span><span style="font-size: 16px; style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">，远离临界值</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">4.72</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:Symbol"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-indent: 32px;">×</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">10<sup>9 </sup>J<sup>1/2</sup></span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">。这说明该预震发生后，仍距未来标志性地震的临界状态尚远，也就是说需要很长时间该标志性地震才会发生。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">涉及到四川的地震区包括汶川、鲜水河、得荣、楚雄、小江、西昌与宜昌地震区（图</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">3</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体">）。由于这些地震区的主震尚未发生，且每个地震区对应的构造块体内某一锁固段断裂后的荷载转移导致的剩余锁固段承受增长的荷载作用，故这些地震区未来的地震活动势必越来越猛。为此，逐渐且有针对性地提高建筑物和构筑物的抗震设防烈度，是防震减灾的关键，应引起有关部门的重视。</span></p><p
